Hey Doc:<br>
     No one is putting their medals (the correct spelling by the way) in your face.  Not many vets are not the Gung Ho always wear my medals and uniform type-sorry the sixties took that out of us.  Our medals were earned the hard way, by being in a horrible world of pain.  Why come to this easy going dialog here and start messing things up!  If you don't like the fact we have medals tough luck, I earned them with blood, sweat and tears.  Few people go to war looking to earn any medals-&quot;Oh Boy feel great today, think I'll go and earn the Silver Star&quot;.  If you don't like the fact we earned medals then GO TO HELL DOC!!!  I'll continue to display them and if you have a problem just try to remove them!  Keep Smiling!
